                                    <div class="text-title">About EquiPPP.com </div>
                                    <div class="panel-body">
                                        <div class="terms-li-padding">

                                            <p>
                                                EquiPPP is a proprietary concept/ideology developed by Mr. D.V.S.S Lakshminaryana, to explore investment opportunities by way of private public participation ("PPP") in projects like Social/civic/infrastructure/environmental related. The project also includes general public and MP/MLA LADS work contributing towards a better society.  Towards this ideology, Mr. Lakshminarayana incubated from concept level to prototype and developed beta version of web portal viz., www.EquiPPP.com herein after called as (EquiPPP) in collaboration with "Bodhtree" as a Technology partner which has enabled the ideology to reach to a global level. This collaboration will help in creating a business model and generate revenues in the future for both EquiPPP and Bodhtree. However, the rights including copyright and other IP rights of the platform would remain with the Management of EquiPPP.
                                            </p></br>
                                            <p>EquiPPP.com is a collaborative platform for both general public, Governments, Corporates, Non Resident Indians, domain experts domicile citizens where they can join together and express/pledge their interests to participate in the projects which has social impact. In other words, EquiPPP as a platform will help in taking Social projects to  global citizens and create an  investment opportunity for investors and help the Government organizations to fulfil the Public interests. The platform will also enable the Government departments to prioritize the Social projects and enable the concerned departments to focus on more social projects that are of public interest by considering key analysis on the Pledges/interests received from the platform.
											</p></br>
 
											<strong>About Bodhtree:</strong></br>
											<p>Bodhtree is a CMMMI Level 5 company and a global IT services provider, headquartered in California with offices across North America, Singapore and India. Founded in 1999, Bodhtree has 800 employees across the globe. The company enables enterprises to transform their business using Cloud CRM and Analytics. In addition, we also provide Digital Solutions and Enterprise Services to Fortune 500 firms and SMEs across healthcare & life sciences, hi-tech manufacturing, education, financial services and government verticals. </p>
